description: Erection of new buildings comprising a mix of uses including replacement community & leisure facilities (library, leisure centre, community centre and joint services centre within class D1/D2) retail store (class A1) , small shop units (class A1-A5 inclusive) business opportunity centre (class B1), health centre (class D1) and 251 dwellings, provision of public and private parking, associated access, servicing arrangements, highway, landscaping and public realm improvements.
